%H A219074 <a href="/index/Rec#order_10">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (11,33,233,13,-31,-657,-321,-288,-64,64).
%F A219074 Empirical: a(n) = 11*a(n-1) +33*a(n-2) +233*a(n-3) +13*a(n-4) -31*a(n-5) -657*a(n-6) -321*a(n-7) -288*a(n-8) -64*a(n-9) +64*a(n-10).
%F A219074 From _Andrew Howroyd_, Jul 17 2026: (Start)
%F A219074 The above empirical formula confirmed using the transfer matrix method.
%F A219074 G.f.: x*(9 + 66*x + 209*x^2 - 128*x^3 - 241*x^4 - 902*x^5 - 525*x^6 - 268*x^7 + 16*x^8 + 64*x^9)/(1 - 11*x - 33*x^2 - 233*x^3 - 13*x^4 + 31*x^5 + 657*x^6 + 321*x^7 + 288*x^8 + 64*x^9 - 64*x^10). (End)
